     INNER JOIN MDocumentos   b ON a.doc = b.codtipodoc  
     LEFT JOIN VIEWpagosPRCMA d ON a.numfactu = d.numfactu  
       WHERE
       a.fechafac ='7/3/2019' AND   a.cod_subgrupo = 'CONSULTA' and  a.statfact=3  and d.desTipoTargeta is  not null and a.usuario='RANGELYS' 
       GROUP BY  
       desTipoTargeta  
       Order by 
       desTipoTargeta
